    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、お疲れ様です。……えっ！？　『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』のお願い事、通ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ thank you for calling… Eh!? My wish for “Miracle☆\nIdol Birthday!” got granted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいに決まってます。クリスマスと誕生日が一緒\nだと、お祝いしてもらってばかりですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I’m happy. Since Christmas and my birthday are\non the same day‚ So I just always get celebrated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私が内緒でみんなを喜ばせたいんです\nあ、サプライズですから、情報の取り扱いには――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For this time‚ I'd like to do a surprise to make everyone happy.\nOh‚ since it’s a surprise‚ please keep this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6999990026,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.333059100002,
